sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler as Pub/Sub Schedule<br/>every 5 min
    participant CF as Cloud Function<br/>checkOverdueReminders
    participant Firestore
    participant FCM
    participant User

    Scheduler->>CF: Trigger
    CF->>Firestore: Query reminders (isCompleted=false, scheduledTime <= now)
    loop For each overdue reminder
        CF->>Firestore: Read users/{userId}.fcmToken
        CF->>FCM: Send reminder notification
        FCM->>User: Push (Reminder: title)
    end